<D>__{co pilot you got this?}
<A>__{the officers nod. one moves toward carter as he dropped in a seat away from alex. terry sits behind carter. the co pilot and attendants start back toward the plane. ms. lewton hustles over to them and an airline representitive.}
<D>__{co pilot no one gets back on board. that's my call.}
<C>__{ms. lewton}
<D>__{please... i've got forty students going to paris...}
<A>__{during these negotiations... camera moves past ms. lewton and the co pilot to the boarding ramp door... clear rivers exits and takes a seat away from the others, aware she is unnoticed in the confusion. camera inches in as she looks up toward...}
<B>__{alex}
<A>__{camera matches the move to him as tod and mr. murnau attempt to calm him down.}
<C>__{tod}
<D>__{it's alright. it's alright. you're off the plane. you're off the plane...}
